creator: Heetch
descriptionHtml:
Heetch is a friendly and professional ride-hailing app. We offer VTC, LVC, taxi or moto-taxi services in several countries.

Heetch drivers are available around the clock when public transit lets you down. We display price estimates before you order and give you the option to choose your favorite payment method! Heetch is shaking things up - we value our drivers, and offer them fair commission rates on their rides.

Heetch, the professional driver app accessible to all

We're here, whether you're looking for a ride day or night. We keep you moving with the same account in multiple countries:

- 🇫🇷In France, Heetch matches you with a driver in seconds at cheaper prices than other VTC or taxi services in Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Lille, Nice, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Nantes and Strasbourg.
- 🇧🇪In Belgium, Heetch is available in Brussels region with LVC
- 🇲🇦In Morocco, we're working with taxis from Casablanca and Marrakech
- 🇩🇿Meet Heetch drivers in Algiers (Algeria)
- Coming soon: 🇦🇴Luanda (Angola), 🇨🇬Brazzaville (Congo)

Low fares, available upfront

Avoid any nasty surprises with Heetch - we show you an estimated cost before you request your ride. Our prices are often lower than taxis and other VTC or LVC apps. Our commission rate is the lowest on the market so our drivers are fairly remunerated. What's more, get 5€ for every friend you refer who starts riding with Heetch. There’s no limit on how much you can earn.

The only app with complete payment flexibility

Heetch lets you pay cash without the hassle of having to save your credit card beforehand. Making splitting the cost with friends easy. No cash? Heetch works with all major credit, debit and prepaid cards. Add a new payment method, and select your favorite before you request a ride.

Heetch, a reliable and safe service wherever you need to go

Got a late party or an early flight? Need to get home after work? Our professional drivers will ride anywhere, any time, without breaking the bank.

What should you choose between subway, RATP buses, Stib trams, CTM, RER or Noctilien? With delays, strikes, it's not easy to get around in the urban jungle! Heetch saves you time and money - know the price upfront and get matched with a VTC, LVC, taxi or moto-taxi driver within seconds. Track the arrival of your driver on the map and go meet them when they're a few minutes away. All Heetch drivers undergo a training program and we check on them on a regular basis.

A more human, accessible and responsible app

We do not only match passengers with drivers. We do it responsibly, by offering low fares to our passengers, and the lowest market commission rates for drivers. We also encourage you to sit in the front seat and have a chat with your driver.

To infinity and beyond!

Heetch matches you with our ride-hailing service in Algeria (Algiers), Belgium (Brussels), in France (Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Lille, Nice, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Nantes and Strasbourg), and in Morocco (Marrakech, Casablanca)!
descriptionShort: Getting your way around town has never been easier!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
“If there is anyone out there who still doubts that Heetch is an app where all bug fixes are possible, who still wonders if the dream of our founders is alive in our time, today is your answer.”
Quote - B.O.

title: Heetch - Ride-hailing app

creator: Heetch
descriptionHtml:
Heetch is a friendly and professional ride-hailing app. We offer VTC, LVC, taxi or moto-taxi services in several countries.

Heetch drivers are available around the clock when public transit lets you down. We display price estimates before you order and give you the option to choose your favorite payment method! We value our drivers and offer them fair commission rates on their rides.

Heetch, the professional driver app accessible to all

We keep you moving with the same account in multiple countries:

- 🇫🇷 In France, Heetch matches you with a driver in seconds at cheaper prices than other VTC or taxi services in Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Lille, Nice, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Nantes, and Strasbourg.
- 🇧🇪 In Belgium, Heetch is available in the Brussels region, Antwerp, Ghent, and Leuven with LVC !
- 🇨🇭 Order a ride in Geneva !
- 🇲🇦 In Morocco, we're working with taxis and VTC from Casablanca, Rabat, and Marrakech !
- 🇩🇿 Meet Heetch drivers in Algiers and Oran (Algeria) !
- 🇦🇴 Now also in Luanda (Angola) !
- 🇸🇳 Our drivers are available in Dakar (Senegal) !
- 🇹🇳 In Tunis you can now order a ride !
- 🇨🇩 Move around Kinshasa with our drivers !
- 🇨🇮 Now available in Abidjan.
- And soon so many new cities !


Low fares, available upfront

Avoid any nasty surprises with Heetch - we show you an estimated cost before you request your ride. Our prices are often lower than taxis and other VTC or LVC apps. Our commission rate is the lowest on the market so our drivers are fairly remunerated. What's more, get rewarded for every friend you refer who starts riding with Heetch. There’s no limit on how much you can earn.

The only app with complete payment flexibility

Heetch lets you pay cash without the hassle of having to save your credit card beforehand. Making splitting the cost with friends easy. No cash? Heetch works with all major credit, debit, and prepaid cards. Add a new payment method, and select your favorite before you request a ride.

Heetch, reliable and safe service wherever you need to go

Got a late party or an early flight? Need to get home after work? Our professional drivers will ride anywhere, any time, without breaking the bank.

With delays, strikes, it's not easy to get around in the urban jungle! Heetch saves you time and money - get matched with a VTC, LVC, taxi or moto-taxi driver within seconds. Track the arrival of your driver on the map and go meet them when they're a few minutes away. All Heetch drivers undergo a training program and we check on them on a regular basis.

To infinity and beyond!

Heetch matches you with our ride-hailing service in Algeria (Algiers, Oran), Belgium (Brussels, Antwerp, Ghent and Leuven), in the Netherlands (Amsterdam, Rotterdam), in Angola (Luanda), in France (Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Lille, Nice, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Nantes and Strasbourg), and in Morocco (Marrakech, Casablanca)!

Heetch drivers are available around the clock when public transit lets you down. We display price estimates before you order and give you the option to choose your favorite payment method! We value our drivers and offer them fair commission rates on their rides.

•Heetch, the professional driver app accessible to all•

We keep you moving with the same account in multiple countries:

- 🇫🇷 In France, Heetch matches you with a driver in seconds at cheaper prices than other VTC or taxi services in Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Montpellier Lille, Nice, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Nantes, and Strasbourg.
- 🇧🇪 In Belgium, Heetch is available in the Brussels region, Antwerp, Ghent, and Leuven with LVC !
- 🇨🇭Order a ride in Geneva !
- 🇲🇦 In Morocco, we're working with taxis and VTC from Casablanca, Rabat, and Marrakech !
- 🇩🇿 Meet Heetch drivers in Algiers and Oran (Algeria) !
- 🇦🇴 Now also in Luanda (Angola) !
- 🇸🇳 Our drivers are available in Dakar (Senegal) !
- 🇹🇳 In Tunis you can now order a ride !
- 🇨🇮 Find our drivers in Abidjan (Ivory Coast)
- 🇨🇩Move around Kinshasa with Heetch.
- And soon so many new cities !

•Low fares, available upfront•

Avoid any nasty surprises with Heetch - we show you an estimated cost before you request your ride. Our prices are often lower than taxis and other VTC or LVC apps. Our commission rate is the lowest on the market so our drivers are fairly remunerated. What's more, get rewarded for every friend you refer who starts riding with Heetch. There’s no limit on how much you can earn.

•The only app with complete payment flexibility•

Heetch lets you pay cash without the hassle of having to save your credit card beforehand. Making splitting the cost with friends easy. No cash? Heetch works with all major credit, debit, and prepaid cards in France, Belgium and Malta. Add a new payment method, and select your favorite before you request a ride.

•Heetch, reliable and safe service wherever you need to go•

Got a late party or an early flight? Need to get home after work? Our professional drivers will ride anywhere, any time, without breaking the bank.

With delays, strikes, it's not easy to get around in the urban jungle! Heetch saves you time and money - get matched with a VTC, LVC or taxi driver within seconds. Track the arrival of your driver on the map and go meet them when they're a few minutes away. Once yourself confortable in the car, you can share your localisation to your friends. All Heetch drivers undergo a training program and we check on them on a regular basis.

•To infinity and beyond!•

Discover new cities by VTC, cab without blowing your budget!
descriptionShort: Heetch, the professional driver app accessible to all

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Did you know ?
Heetch is available in 11 countries worldwide, including 8 countries in Africa!

For this new version our teams have focused on correcting a few bugs.
Your experience with Heetch will only be better!

•Heetch, reliable and safe service wherever you need to go•

•To infinity and beyond!•

Discover new cities by VTC, cab without blowing your budget!

title: Heetch - Ride-hailing app

creator: Heetch
descriptionHtml:
•Heetch is a friendly and professional ride-hailing app.• We offer VTC, LVC, taxi services in several countries.

Heetch drivers are available around the clock when public transit lets you down. We display price estimates before you order and give you the option to choose your favorite payment method! We value our drivers and offer them fair commission rates on their rides.

•Heetch, the professional driver app accessible to all•

We keep you moving with the same account in multiple countries:

- 🇫🇷 In France, Heetch matches you with a driver in seconds at cheaper prices than other VTC or taxi services in Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Montpellier Lille, Nice, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Nantes, and Strasbourg.
- 🇧🇪 In Belgium, Heetch is available in the Brussels region, Antwerp, Ghent, and Leuven with LVC !
- 🇩🇿 Meet Heetch drivers in Algiers and Oran (Algeria) !
- 🇦🇴 Now also in Luanda (Angola) !
- 🇸🇳 Our drivers are available in Dakar (Senegal) !
- 🇨🇮 Find our drivers in Abidjan (Ivory Coast)
- 🇲🇱 Move around Bamako with Heetch.
- And soon so many new cities !

•Low fares, available upfront•

Avoid any nasty surprises with Heetch - we show you an estimated cost before you request your ride. Our prices are often lower than taxis and other VTC or LVC apps. Our commission rate is the lowest on the market so our drivers are fairly remunerated. What's more, get rewarded for every friend you refer who starts riding with Heetch. There’s no limit on how much you can earn.

•The only app with complete payment flexibility•

Heetch lets you pay cash without the hassle of having to save your credit card beforehand. Making splitting the cost with friends easy. No cash? Heetch works with all major credit, debit, and prepaid cards in France, Belgium and Malta. Add a new payment method, and select your favorite before you request a ride.

•Heetch, reliable and safe service wherever you need to go•

Got a late party or an early flight? Need to get home after work? Our professional drivers will ride anywhere, any time, without breaking the bank.

With delays, strikes, it's not easy to get around in the urban jungle! Heetch saves you time and money - get matched with a VTC, LVC or taxi driver within seconds. Track the arrival of your driver on the map and go meet them when they're a few minutes away. Once yourself confortable in the car, you can share your localisation to your friends. All Heetch drivers undergo a training program and we check on them on a regular basis.

•To infinity and beyond!•

Discover new cities by VTC, cab without blowing your budget!
